#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/mastiff.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Keen Hearing and Smell.** The mastiff has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) "
"checks that rely on hearing or smell. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/mastiff.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions    \n"
"**Bite.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"4 (1d6 + 1) piercing damage. If the target is a creature, it must succeed on "
"a DC 11 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/mastiff.md:27
msgid ""
"### Description Mastiffs are impressive hounds prized by humanoids for their "
"loyalty and keen senses. Mastiffs can be trained as guard dogs, hunting "
"dogs, and war dogs. Halflings and other Small humanoids ride them as mounts."
msgstr ""
